                     <interp inst="t17840915-12-person251" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I apprehended the prisoner, and went by his direction, and found the soap under his sister's bed; the prisoner lodged there as he told me.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy, I have a wife and several children.</p>
               <p>
